{"tid":1977771,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於水門雞 對 阿玉冰室 既指控 既整理","createTime":"2020-04-18T08:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T17:45:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d30de33ee7635eac6b7bbf97097e850e616c8f7b","tid":1977771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"TLDR:<br />\n- 除非捉咗嗰幾個老黑拷問否則永遠唔會有答案<br />\n- 表面供詞，證據，非常弱，案情亦不合情理<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- 個人結論：當係誤會一場，兩邊繼續支持</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前水門雞既指責<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OC0dtzb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOC0dtzb.png&h=c38c1a75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hao26cP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhao26cP.png&h=3b27937e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OpLthjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOpLthjw.png&h=53808f72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVYVGMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVYVGMd.png&h=95040531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水門雞既回應，仲有一段聲稱阿玉老闆既錄音<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch5thL0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh5thL0.png&h=fc21e050&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GG6wfxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGG6wfxL.png&h=091460c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/水門泰式雞飯專門店-737261133131865/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%E6%B0%B4%E9%96%80%E6%B3%B0%E5%BC%8F%E9%9B%9E%E9%A3%AF%E5%B0%88%E9%96%80%E5%BA%97-737261133131865%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal%26mt_nav%3D0&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=874995a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/水門泰式雞飯專門店-737261133131865/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0</a>"},{"pid":"72e05cabf2d5c63abb55dcb4403643dd1dbd2773","tid":1977771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"1. 阿玉冰室係一個&lsquo;黃店老闆&lsquo;群組公開話'打柒&lsquo;水門雞，然後當晚就叫人𣺉紅油，𣺉埋隔離<br />\n佢然後自己親自落去扮好人幫手清理<br />\n唔怕俾人圍毆<br />\n唔怕水門攞段錄音當面指證？<br />\n<br />\n2. 按水門講法，2:00俾人冧紅沖<br />\n油<br />\n但段錄音時間係2:4x<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HbakTr5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbakTr5.png&h=57e99b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3&rsquo; 段錄音冇show 阿玉電話號碼<br />\n水門fb 下面有人話阿玉老細把聲唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n4. 有咁堅既證據點解唔一早攞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果水門可以cap 圖 show 電話頭4-5冧把係阿玉既<br />\n（del contact再cap 圖）<br />\n有其他同group&rsquo;黃店老闆&rsquo;講段錄音係真<br />\n咁就好明顯阿玉有嫌疑"},{"pid":"66e92e882c460240793651aad4f412089e4a4b35","tid":1977771,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"繼續買，兩間都狂買。"},{"pid":"5c29603af33c8610d7373ed0fb3559a006a8d97b","tid":1977771,"uid":102835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"段錄音淨係證明到亞玉好撚嬲講粗口屌老母，根本冇證據證明到亞玉搵鄉黑搞水門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要亞玉搵證據證明返自己係清白？大陸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忠輝同有其他人都話見到班鄉黑一直企喺忠輝對面間診所啦<br />\n仲有堆花邊新聞（開分身、華叔）真係冇眼睇<br />\n<br />\n1. 水門個老細咁撚串，冇可能叫佢認低威<br />\n2. 亞玉連認證都摵走埋擺明想以後河水不犯井水<br />\n3. 最無辜係忠輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無啦啦都要畀人話偏幫<br />\n<br />\n成件事冇得再有突破架喇，就咁完啦<br />\n<br />\n見到群組同fb好多人都話唔想再睇依場鬧劇<br />\n希望兩位老細一人少句唔好再搞是非<br />\n唔好再搞咩黃店KOL，打兩句發起網民圍攻自己人...仲有好多小店等大家支持"},{"pid":"b317f6c1b27ead093676c8f4d558e30d600dd740","tid":1977771,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c29603af33c8610d7373ed0fb3559a006a8d97b","tid":1977771,"uid":102835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"段錄音淨係證明到亞玉好撚嬲講粗口屌老母，根本