"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=4a33aff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"717ceccbac0908790e5ee589f8af8853989dc4a6","tid":1977771,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c9391d631a5b5a13c52fbac8d37e53004a5ed0","tid":1977771,"uid":127176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd2299bfde05be3a4f7ca95e3b0f428c87e7ea62","tid":1977771,"uid":264326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"72e05cabf2d5c63abb55dcb4403643dd1dbd2773","tid":1977771,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"